Shadows Spider is a realtime 3d rendering engine built around OpenGL 4.5 and GLFW.

FEATURES:
- intuitive ui (NOT PUT BACK IN YET)
- transform gizmos (NOT PUT BACK IN YET)
- frustum culling (NOT PUT BACK IN YET)
- deferred shading, PBR, SSR, BOIT
- C++11
- obj and texture files located at https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5Eg0nuMXxh9b0ZPWWxQR1VneFE/view?usp=sharing
- Windows

HOW TO BUILD:
- GLFW 3.2.1
- glew 1.13.0
- GLM

Demo vid at https://youtu.be/ll6h43GsIdM

